template.name: SNMP HP v1910-48G
template.description:
## Overview
This template expanded the original 24 ports template to 48 ports published by Павел Яковлев and made compatible with Zabbix 2.0.x+
It is necessary to set:
* {$SNMP\_COMMUNITY} - **public** is the default value for read-only and **private** for read-write. * {$SNMP\_PORT} - The value **161** is the default for SNMP port.
The template was tested in Zabbix:
* 2.0.6 * 2.2.7
## Author
Rômulo Mendes Figueiredo
